Say '''Allen''' et kumalima ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Northern Samar]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 23,738 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 47.6 sq. km. Sikato et walad unaan ya distrito. Say zip code to et 6405.	
															
